    About this item

    • 20W PD Fast Charging: UGREEN USB C charger supports up to 20W power delivery to charge your new iPhone 12 from 0% to 58% just within 30mins.
    • Pocket Size: 50% smaller than a standard 20W iPhone USB C wall charger, which won't jam the other ports on the wall outlet, you'll have access to fast charging wherever you go.
    • One for All: Perfectly fits the charging needs of iPhone 12/12 Pro/12 Pro Max, also compatible with AirPods, MagSafe Duo, iPhone 11/11 Pro/11 Pro Max/XS/XR/X/8 Plus, iPad, Galaxy S10/S9, Google Pixel, Nintendo Switch, LG G7/V50, and more.
    • Safety Wall Charger: With the intelligent chip inside, UGREEN 20W power adapter matches the devices current automatically. Over-current, over-voltage, and short-circuit protection effectively protect your devices from damage and ensure safer charging overnight.
    • Meticulous Design: Square design, the center of gravity is in the middle, making the USB C charger more stably when plugged into the outlet.

    Product Description

    UGREEN 20W PD USB C Charger -- Smaller Yet 3X Faster to charge your iPhone 12 from 0% to 58% within 30mins

    Power Delivery 3.0 Fast Charging

    • Equipped with a USB-C power supply port and equipped with a 20W power supply, it can provide full-speed charging for mobile phones, tablets, and more compatible devices.
    • Unparalleled speed: Compared with the original 5W charger, charging the iPhone 12 and previous iPhone models can be up to 3 times faster.
    • Space-saving design: 50% smaller than standard iPhone 12 USB-C power adapter.

    To achieve fast charging:

    • In addition to using this fast charger, your charging cables and mobile phones also need to support fast charging protocol.
    • You can use an extra USB C to C cable(Not included) or USB C to Lightning cable(Not included) working with this USB-C wall charger.

    High-Speed Charging

    Equipped with a 20W USB-C Power Delivery port, more up to 3 faster than with an original charger.

    Widely Compatibility

    Compatible for AirPods, for Nintendo Switch, for MagSafe, for iPhone, Galaxy, Google Pixel, HTC, LG, for true wireless earbuds, ect.

    Compact Size

    A 50% smaller wall charger is equipped with international voltage compatibility. Ideal for travel anywhere in the world.
